<sect1 id="_mesh_from_unity_1autotoc_md28">
<title>Intro</title>
<para>In this tutorial we&apos;ll be using the project created in the first tutorial: <ref refid="_unity_project_setup" kindref="compound">Project Setup</ref>, and we&apos;ll be using concepts and code covered in the previous guides.</para>
<para>In this guide we will cover:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Assigning a game object to a script so it can be referenced by code.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Accessing the components of a Game Object</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transforming MeshInfo instances to Z-Up</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="_mesh_from_unity_1autotoc_md29">
<title>Scene Setup</title>
